==歐洲議會訂為紀念日、歐安組織支持==
2008年4月，[[歐洲聯盟理事會主席國|歐洲聯盟理事會主席國]]斯洛文尼亞和[[歐洲聯盟委員會|歐洲聯盟委員會]]舉辦[[歐洲極權政權所犯罪行公聽會|歐洲極權政權所犯罪行公聽會]]，旨在教育公眾，使公眾提高對極權政權罪行的警覺<ref name="EU-Hearing-2008">{{cite web |url= http://europa.eu/rapid/pressReleasesAction.do?reference=MEMO/08/230&type=HTML&aged=0&language=EN&guiLanguage=en |title= European hearing on crimes committed by totalitarian regimes |author=  |date= 08/04/2008 |work=  |publisher= {{tsl|en|Europa.eu||Europa.eu}} |archiveurl= https://www.webcitation.org/5yfV7NJqF?url=http://europa.eu/rapid/pressReleasesAction.do?reference=MEMO%2F08%2F230 |archivedate= 2011-05-14 |accessdate= 2011-05-10 |quote=  |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>[http://www.mp.gov.si/fileadmin/mp.gov.si/pageuploads/2005/PDF/publikacije/Crimes_committed_by_Totalitarian_Regimes.pdf Crimes Committed by Totalitarian Regimes] {{Wayback|url=http://www.mp.gov.si/fileadmin/mp.gov.si/pageuploads/2005/PDF/publikacije/Crimes_committed_by_Totalitarian_Regimes.pdf |date=20120302035902 }}. Slovenian Presidency of the Council of the European Union.</ref>。

2008年6月3日，由[[捷克政府|捷克政府]]發起，[[瓦茨拉夫·哈維爾|瓦茨拉夫·哈維爾]]等人簽署的《[[关于欧洲良知和谴责共产主义罪行布拉格宣言|布拉格宣言]]》，提議8月23日訂為正式紀念日，國際組織和一些國家於同年響應。《布拉格宣言》總結了2008年6月2至3日在[[捷克參議院|捷克參議院]]舉行的歐洲良心與共產主義會議<ref name="declaration-text">{{cite web |url= http://www.praguedeclaration.org/ |title= Prague Declaration – Declaration Text |author=  |date= 3 June 2008 |work=  |publisher= {{tsl|en|Institute for Information on the Crimes of Communism||Institute for Information on the Crimes of Communism}} |accessdate= 28 January 2010 |archive-date= 2008-09-29 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20080929021343/http://www.praguedeclaration.org/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

2008年8月23日，409名歐洲議會議員簽署宣言，將8月23日訂為歐洲史太林主義和納粹主義受害人紀念日<ref name="EP-Declaration">{{cite web |url= http://www.europarl.europa.eu/sides/getDoc.do?pubRef=-//EP//TEXT+TA+P6-TA-2008-0439+0+DOC+XML+V0//EN |title= Declaration of the European Parliament on the proclamation of 23 August as European Day of Remembrance for Victims of Stalinism and Nazism |author= |date= |work= |publisher= {{tsl|en|Europa.eu||Europa.eu}} | archiveurl  = | archivedate = |accessdate= 2011-05-10 | quote= }}</ref>。宣言指出：「史太林主義和納粹主義在侵略範疇所犯的大規模驅逐、謀殺和奴役，屬於戰爭罪行和反人道罪行。在國際法下，法定時效不應用於戰爭罪行和反人道罪行。<ref name="EP-Declaration" />」

2009年4月2日，歐洲議會關於歐洲良心與極權主義的決議案，呼籲其成員國和其他歐洲國家制訂歐洲史太林主義和納粹主義受害人紀念日，決議案獲533對44票通過，另有33票棄權<ref name="EP-Resolution">{{cite web |url= http://www.europarl.europa.eu/sides/getDoc.do?pubRef=-//EP//TEXT+TA+P6-TA-2009-0213+0+DOC+XML+V0//EN |title= European Parliament resolution of 2 April 2009 on European conscience and totalitarianism |author= |date= |work= |publisher= {{tsl|en|Europa.eu||Europa.eu}} | archiveurl  = | archivedate = |accessdate= 2011-05-10 | quote= }}</ref>。

2009年7月3日，[[歐洲安全和合作組織|歐洲安全和合作組織]]（歐安組織）採納[[維爾紐斯宣言|維爾紐斯宣言]]，支持將8月23日訂為國際極權主義紀念日，促請其成員國提高對極權政權罪行的警覺<ref name="OSCE-Declaration">{{cite web |url= http://www.oscepa.org/images/stories/documents/activities/1.Annual%20Session/2009_Vilnius/Final_Vilnius_Declaration_ENG.pdf |title= Vilnius Declaration of the OSCE Parliamentary Assembly and resolutions adopted at the eighteenth annual session |author=  |date= 29 June to 3 July 2009 |work=  |publisher= {{tsl|en|Parliamentary Assembly of the Organization for Security and Co-operation in Europe||Parliamentary Assembly of the Organization for Security and Co-operation in Europe}} (OSCEPA) |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20100111155028/http://www.oscepa.org/images/stories/documents/activities/1.Annual%20Session/2009_Vilnius/Final_Vilnius_Declaration_ENG.pdf |archivedate= 2010-01-11 |accessdate= 2011-05-14 |quote=  |dead-url= yes }}</ref>。

繼歐洲議會制訂歐洲史太林主義和納粹主義受害人紀念日，歐洲議會議長[[漢斯-格特·珀特林|漢斯-格特·珀特林]]在2009年感謝[[立陶宛|立陶宛]]、[[拉脫維亞|拉脫維亞]]和[[愛沙尼亞|愛沙尼亞]]三國政府，因為他們努力使西歐認識蘇聯極權主義。珀特林引述[[漢娜·鄂蘭|漢娜·鄂蘭]]的《[[極權主義的起源|極權主義的起源]]》，總括「兩種極權制度──史太林主義和納粹主義──是很類似和惡劣的」<ref name="eurolt">{{cite web |url= http://www.euro.lt/en/news/lithuanias-membership-in-the-eu/news/5537/?print=1 |title= Baltic States opened Western Europe's eyes on Soviet Union totalitarianism -- EP chairman in Vilnius |author=  |date= 2009-04-28 |work=  |publisher= BNS |archiveurl= https://www.webcitation.org/5yf88YFCY?url=http://www.euro.lt/en/news/lithuanias-membership-in-the-eu/news/5537/?print=1 |archivedate= 2011-05-14 |accessdate= 2011-05-10 |quote=  |dead-url= yes }}</ref>。

[[歐洲人民黨|歐洲人民黨]]主席[[約瑟夫·道爾|約瑟夫·道爾]]指出：「2009年是深具意義的一年，因我們同時慶祝[[北約組織|北約組織]]創立和冷戰開始60週年，以及[[柏林圍牆|柏林圍牆]]倒下和冷戰結束20週年。因此我們建議設立全歐洲紀念日，使歐洲從其極權──包括納粹黨和共產黨──的後遺中復元。<ref name="neurope-daul">{{cite web |url= http://www.neurope.eu/articles/93920.php |title= A day to condemn Communism |author=  |date= 6 April 2009 |work=  |publisher= {{tsl|en|New Europe (newspaper)||New Europe}} |archiveurl= https://www.webcitation.org/5ymbQkAU4?url=http://www.neurope.eu/articles/93920.php |archivedate= 2011-05-18 |accessdate= 2011-05-16 |quote=  |dead-url= yes }}</ref>」

2011年6月10日，由所有歐盟成員國的司法和內政部門首長組成的歐盟[[歐盟理事會|法律和內政事務司]]，指出「提高公眾對極權政權犯下罪行的警覺的重要性，以及促進歐洲聯盟內此等罪行的共同記憶的重要性，並指出此舉對於防止極權思想復甦和再生的重要性」，並邀請成員國考慮怎樣在8月23日紀念極權政權受害人<ref name="JusticeHomeAffairs">{{cite web |url= http://www.consilium.europa.eu/uedocs/cms_data/docs/pressdata/en/jha/122521.pdf |title= Council conclusions on the memory of the crimes committed by totalitarian regimes in Europe |author=  |date=  |work=  |publisher= [[欧洲联盟理事会|欧洲联盟理事会]] |archiveurl= https://www.webcitation.org/5zO7mIFTb?url=http://www.consilium.europa.eu/uedocs/cms_data/docs/pressdata/en/jha/122521.pdf |archivedate= 2011-06-12 |accessdate= 2011-06-12 |quote=  |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

2011年8月23日，歐盟理事會主席國波蘭舉辦會議，引述6月10日結束的法律和內政事務司和歐盟的[[斯德哥爾摩計劃|斯德哥爾摩計劃]]，斯德哥爾摩計劃強調「紀念共同歷史對於認識當代歐洲是必須的」。歐洲官員採納《華沙關於歐洲紀念極權政權受害人紀念日宣言》<ref name="PolEUPresidency">{{cite web |url= http://pl2011.eu/en/content/conference-european-day-remembrance-victims-totalitarian-regimes |title= Conference – The European Day of Remembrance of the victims of the totalitarian regimes |author=  |date=  |work=  |publisher= [[歐洲聯盟理事會主席國|歐洲聯盟理事會主席國]] |archiveurl= https://www.webcitation.org/61A2DcR66?url=http://pl2011.eu/en/content/conference-european-day-remembrance-victims-totalitarian-regimes |archivedate= 2011-08-23 |accessdate= 2011-08-23 |quote=  |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref name="EUCal2">{{cite web |url= http://europa.eu/eucalendar/event/id/243051/mode/standalone |title= European day of remembrance of the victims of the totalitarian regimes |author= |date= |work= |publisher= {{tsl|en|Europa.eu||Europa.eu}} |accessdate= 2011-08-23 | quote       = }}</ref>，申明極權政權受害人的痛苦不會被遺忘<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.todayonline.com/BreakingNews/EDC110823-0001116/Europe-remembers-victims-of-Stalinism-and-Nazism |title=Europe remembers victims of Stalinism and Nazism |publisher=TODAYonline |date= |accessdate=2011-08-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120202120857/http://www.todayonline.com/BreakingNews/EDC110823-0001116/Europe-remembers-victims-of-Stalinism-and-Nazism |archive-date=2012-02-02 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。宣言指出「不論是哪個種類和思想形態，極權政權在歐洲的罪行都必須認識和譴責」。司法部長[[克日什托夫·克維亞特科夫斯基|克日什托夫·克維亞特科夫斯基]]表示，「《華沙宣言》是所有歐盟成員國一致同意，我們需竭盡所能，防範極權主義在歐洲大家庭內的所有國家中復甦。<ref name="thenewspl2">{{cite web |url= http://www.thenews.pl/1/10/Artykul/53857,-Warsaw-declaration-against-totalitarianism-signed |title= Warsaw declaration against totalitarianism signed |author=  |date=  |work=  |publisher= thenews.pl |archiveurl= https://www.webcitation.org/61B0dqkQk?url=http://www.thenews.pl/1/10/Artykul/53857,-Warsaw-declaration-against-totalitarianism-signed |archivedate= 2011-08-24 |accessdate= 2011-08-23 |quote=  |dead-url= no }}</ref>」歐盟司法專員[[維維亞娜·雷丁|維維亞娜·雷丁]]指出：
{{cquote|極權政權否認人性尊嚴，侵犯以民主和法治所建成的社會的基本權利。我們對於這些罪行的受害人和其家人，必須表達同情、理解和認同他們所承受的痛苦。極權政權下的每位受害人都有相同的人性尊嚴，應得到我們所有人的公義、紀念和認同。<ref name="EU-Commission-on-23-August">{{cite web|author=|url=http://europa.eu/rapid/pressReleasesAction.do?reference=MEMO/11/564&format=HTML&aged=0&language=EN&guiLanguage=en|title=Statement by Vice-President Viviane Reding, EU Justice Commissioner on the Europe-wide Day of Remembrance for the victims of all totalitarian and authoritarian regimes|publisher={{tsl|en|europa.eu||europa.eu}}|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/64tQhTqUk?url=http://europa.eu/rapid/pressReleasesAction.do?reference=MEMO%2F11%2F564|date=23 August 2011|accessdate=2011-08-23|archivedate=2012-01-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>}}

